title: Backstage at Women Tell All
description:
Right after leaving the stage with Chris Harrison, Peter and the women are talking to “Bachelor Happy Hour.” Rachel sits down with Alayah, Kelsey, Lexi, Shiann, Sydney, Tammy and Victoria P. to talk about the endless drama this season and get their predictions on how it will all end for Peter.

Then, Peter on Madison revealing so late in the process that she is saving herself for marriage. 

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
